    "body": "# Pull Request\n\n## Description\nThis PR introduces several code quality improvements, enhances type safety, and adds new utilities for performance monitoring and optimized component loading.\n\nKey changes include:\n- Refactoring `any` types in `App.tsx` and `NewContentAdvertisingBanner.tsx` to use specific interfaces.\n- Removing unused imports across various components.\n- Implementing `lazyLoadComponents.ts` for efficient, retry-enabled component lazy loading with prefetch capabilities.\n- Introducing `enhancedPerformanceMonitor.ts` to track Core Web Vitals (LCP, FID, CLS) and other performance metrics.\n\n## Type of Change\n- [ ] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\n- [x] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)\n- [ ] Breaking change (fix or feature that would cause existing functionality to not work as expected)\n- [ ] Documentation update\n- [x] Refactoring (no functional changes)\n- [x] Performance improvement\n- [ ] Security fix\n\n## Testing\n- [x] I have tested this change locally\n- [ ] I have added tests for this change\n- [x] All existing tests pass\n- [ ] I have tested the build process\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] My code follows the project's style guidelines\n- [x] I have performed a self-review of my code\n- [x] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas\n- [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation\n- [x] My changes generate no new warnings\n- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works\n- [x] New and existing unit tests pass locally with my changes\n- [ ] Any dependent changes have been merged and published\n\n## Screenshots (if applicable)\nN/A\n\n## Additional Notes\nThese changes significantly improve the codebase's maintainability, type safety, and lay the groundwork for better performance monitoring and optimization. Linting warnings related to `any` types and unused imports have been addressed.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-92430f7f-66df-4b99-bab7-5975b06670ec\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-92430f7f-66df-4b99-bab7-5975b06670ec\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\"></picture></a>\n\n",
